Clément Ader Institute

   Welcome to the Clément Ader Institute (ICA, CNRS UMR 5312) website.
   ICA is a research laboratory that focuses on the study of structures,
   systems and mechanical processes. Our activity sectors are in the
   mechanical industries with a particular focus on aerospace, space,
   transportation and energy. Our work usually focus on behavior modeling,
   instrumentation and the study of the durability of the structures or
   products considered. A large part of our research focus on composite
   materials, which play today an important role in structures.


